  "description": "This image depicts a small, rocky stream flowing through a lush, green forest. Water cascades down a series of small waterfalls and around smooth, moss-covered rocks. The stream bed is filled with dark, rounded stones.  Tall, slender trees rise in the background, their trunks partially obscured by the dense foliage.  The forest floor is covered in vibrant green moss and ferns, creating a rich, textured landscape.  Sunlight filters through the canopy, creating a dappled light effect. Fallen branches and roots are visible alongside the stream, adding to the natural, wild feel of the scene.",
